    authors:
      - family-names: "Fuhrman"
        given-names: "David R."
    title: "Matlab implementation of the third-order, multi-directional, irregular wave theory of Madsen & Fuhrman (2012, J. Fluid Mech. 698, 304-334)"
    url: "https://data.dtu.dk/articles/code/Matlab_implementation_of_the_third-order_multi-directional_irregular_wave_theory_of_Madsen_Fuhrman_2012_J_Fluid_Mech_698_304-334_/22060124"
    date-released: 2024-02-08
